         <xocs:funding-text>Mark Powell and Pavla R\u016F\u017Ekov\u00E1 supported us during the field work. Ji\u0159\u00ED Kub\u00E1sek calculated habitat areas and ecotone lengths. The British Lichen Society generously provided their database. This study was supported by the long-term research development Project RVO 67985939 and project TA\u010CR SS01010270 . </xocs:funding-text>
