         <ce:floats>
            <ce:figure id="f0005">
               <ce:label>Fig. 1</ce:label>
               <ce:caption id="ca0005">
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0005" view="all">Locations of the eleven studied hotspots in Great Britain; description of the sites is in Table S1.</ce:simple-para>
               </ce:caption>
               <ce:alt-text role="short" id="al0005">Fig. 1</ce:alt-text>
               <ce:link id="lk0005" locator="gr1" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="pii:S000632072100495X/gr1" xlink:role="http://data.elsevier.com/vocabulary/ElsevierContentTypes/23.4"/>
            </ce:figure>
            <ce:figure id="f0010">
               <ce:label>Fig. 2</ce:label>
               <ce:caption id="ca0010">
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0010" view="all">Linear regression between total species richness and number of frequent, casual and rare species, respectively, in eleven studied hotspots of epiphytic and epixylic lichens in Great Britain. For each regression, the coefficient of determination (R<ce:sup loc="post">2</ce:sup>) and symbol of significance at the level <ce:italic>p</ce:italic> &lt; 0.001 (***), <ce:italic>p</ce:italic> &lt; 0.01 (**) or <ce:italic>p</ce:italic> &lt; 0.05 (*) are displayed.</ce:simple-para>
               </ce:caption>
               <ce:alt-text role="short" id="al0010">Fig. 2</ce:alt-text>
               <ce:link id="lk0010" locator="gr2" xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="pii:S000632072100495X/gr2" xlink:role="http://data.elsevier.com/vocabulary/ElsevierContentTypes/23.4"/>
            </ce:figure>
            <ce:figure id="f0015">
