               <ce:caption id="ca0015">
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0015" view="all">Dissimilarity in species composition partitioned to components of species turnover (Simpson dissimilarity) and nestedness for rare, casual, frequent and total epiphytic and epixylic lichen species recorded in eleven hotspots in Great Britain. The symbol *** indicates significance at the level <ce:italic>p</ce:italic> &lt; 0.001, ** <ce:italic>p</ce:italic> &lt; 0.01 and * <ce:italic>p</ce:italic> &lt; 0.05.</ce:simple-para>
