                  <ce:para id="p0110" view="all">Mark Powell and Pavla Růžková supported us during the field work. Jiří Kubásek calculated habitat areas and ecotone lengths. The British Lichen Society generously provided their database. This study was supported by the long-term research development Project <ce:grant-sponsor id="gts0005" sponsor-id="https://doi.org/10.13039/100013405" xlink:type="simple" xlink:role="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/linking-roles/grant-sponsor">RVO</ce:grant-sponsor> 
                     <ce:grant-number id="gtn0005" refid="gts0005">67985939</ce:grant-number> and project <ce:grant-sponsor id="gts1005" xlink:type="simple" xlink:role="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/linking-roles/grant-sponsor">TAČR</ce:grant-sponsor> 
                     <ce:grant-number id="gtn1005" refid="gts1005">SS01010270</ce:grant-number>.</ce:para>
               </ce:section>
            </ce:acknowledgment>
