                  <ce:para id="p0120" view="all">Supplementary data to this article can be found online at <ce:inter-ref xlink:href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.biocon.2021.109443" id="ir0005" xlink:type="simple">https://doi.org/10.1016/j.biocon.2021.109443</ce:inter-ref>.</ce:para>
